# [goecharger API (lite)](https://github.com/bkogler/goecharger-api-lite)
Lightweight Python API for accessing modern go-eCharger EV wallboxes using local HTTP API v2

[go-eCharger](https://go-e.com) models:
* Gemini
* Gemini flex
* HOMEfix
* HOME+

# Table of contents
